---
title: Grilled Montreal-Spiced Lamb Chops and Asparagus with Nectarine-Tomato Salad and Grilled Naan
description: Fire up the grill! We've packed this meal with all the best flavours of the season; juicy nectarines, tender asparagus and Montreal-spiced lamb chops. Enjoy!
